# Microscopes

The Cell Observatory houses state-of-the-art microscopes for various imaging applications. They are located at different locations at the university and hosted by different institutes.

[:material-view-grid: Browse by Category](microscope_overview.md){ .md-button } [:material-table: Explore microscope database](https://baserow.io/public/grid/oGrkNUBEQGqCGMolgGFjjBQYcDqQZ3wMWnmmiV8g5IM){ .md-button target="_blank" }

<div class="microscope-filter-bar">
  <div class="search-wrapper">
    <input type="search" id="microscope-search" placeholder="Search microscopes..." />
    <button id="microscope-clear" type="button" aria-label="Clear search">&times;</button>
  </div>
  <span id="result-count"></span>
</div>

<div id="microscope-filters">
  <div class="filter-group">
    <span class="filter-group-label">Type:</span>
    {% for t in types %}
    <span class="filter-chip" data-category="type" data-value="{{ t }}">{{ t }}</span>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <div class="filter-group">
    <span class="filter-group-label">Institute:</span>
    {% for inst in institutes %}
    <span class="filter-chip" data-category="institute" data-value="{{ inst }}">{{ inst }}</span>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>

<table id="mic-data-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Name</th>
      <th>Institute</th>
      <th>Type</th>
      <th>Location</th>
      <th>Applications</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for mic in microscopes %}
    <tr data-type="{{ mic.microscope_type | lower }}" data-institute="{{ mic.institute | lower }}">
      <td><a href="../mic_pages/{{ mic.slug }}/">{{ mic.name }}</a></td>
      <td>{{ mic.institute }}</td>
      <td><span class="mic-type mic-type--{{ mic.microscope_type | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}">{{ mic.microscope_type }}</span></td>
      <td>{{ mic.location }}</td>
      <td>{{ mic.applications }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>
